main event: On April 8, 1963, a UFO was detected near Iceland, visible on radar and described as a bright object.
interesting points: The object was observed for a duration of 1-2 minutes,The radar could not lock onto the target, indicating it was difficult to track,The object disappeared at a 15-degree elevation, possibly due to moonlight interference,There were multiple sightings in the vicinity, including from the crew of a British merchant ship,The object was described as a large bright light, much brighter than stars.
sighted object: a bright light in the sky
witness description: crew of a British merchant ship
